snippet.title: Mousey ~ Sly-inspired 3D Platformer (Full Early Playthrough)
snippet.description:
another game by my buddy fr4nk0, which I once again had the courtesy of making music for. I made tracks for the lobby and the training level.

the objective in each level is to collect a set amount of cheese and cheese keys which will open a certain chest inside the fridge

this game is coming out 20th of January on his itch.io site:
https://fr4nk0.itch.io/mousey

check out the soundtrack:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLjHV5qg9vBwvtXBr8GEM1kZhauUSPIfpG

(note: the camera turning slightly isn't some cinematic effect, it's my fucking dualsense drifting)

Timestamps:
0:00 ~ Training
2:27 ~ Kitchen
6:35 ~ Living Room
11:15 ~ Bedroom
16:18 ~ Fridge
19:11 ~ Ending + Secrets
